THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS
================================================================================

This repository REDISTRIBUTES NO third-party source code. The repository
contains only norxs-authored files.

One third-party component is fetched AT BUILD TIME, for the host test build
only, and is never linked into the production library (zzta_core):

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Component : GoogleTest (googletest)
Version   : v1.14.0 (pinned by commit hash in CMakeLists.txt)
Origin    : https://github.com/google/googletest
License   : BSD-3-Clause
Copyright : Copyright 2008, Google Inc. All rights reserved.
Usage     : Test framework for the zzta_tests executable. Fetched via CMake
            FetchContent only when ZZTA_BUILD_TESTS=ON and not cross-compiling.
            TEST DEPENDENCY ONLY — no GoogleTest code is compiled into, linked
            against, or distributed with the zzta_core production library.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Build-environment toolchains (GCC, Clang, arm-none-eabi-gcc, newlib, CMake,
Ninja, cppcheck, clang-tidy, gcovr) are used as tools and are neither modified
nor redistributed by this repository.

